column5: I will be going up there on Saturday the 19th and wondering how the lake levels are and how the fishing is.

Hi PJM, I'm not sure how the water level is as I never asked but a few of my buddies have been doing well there. I have a few maps that are online of Lac Des Milles Lacs if you are interested. Roger mayer.
Mahumba Thanks for the reply and yes I am interested in some on-line maps because I would like some updated maps of the lake. Hope to here form you soon..........PJM
Hi PJM, Email me at [email protected] Roger Mayer.
